text: Nine days before Brexit Day, and I've been here before... Britain is hurtling towards homelessness just the way I did last year. https://wp.me/p9Z5g0-7G
author: KatyEvansBush

text: Hundreds of thousands of people on housing benefit are being locked out of homes they could otherwise afford. It’s totally wrong. I’ve signed @Shelter’s petition to #EndDSSdiscrimination. Join me!
author: KatyEvansBush

text: It's a sunny Sunday afternoon with no WIND and my virus appears to be lifting, & I just think my deathbed words will be:  I'M SO BEHIND WITH EVERYTHING
author: KatyEvansBush
